image_analysis.description: A photograph of a luxurious, private salon or dressing room. The room features a built-in vanity with a large mirror, several smaller mirrors, and built-in cabinetry in a cream or off-white color. There is a professional-style white salon chair with black armrests positioned on a black floor mat. Two pink and white striped upholstered chairs are also visible. On the vanity, there are various bottles, containers, and a telephone. A chandelier with a triangular light fixture hangs from the ceiling. To the left, a rack of belts is visible. In the background, there is a doorway leading to another mirrored area with a small sign containing the letter 'Q'.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot with a focus on a vanity and salon chair.

stamps_or_markings: Evidence tag/sign with the letter 'Q' visible in the background mirror reflection.
Bates stamp 'EFTA00001060' at the bottom right.
